{
  "page": "Durran Durrandon",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Durran Durrandon</b> is the name of several <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm Kings</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>, founded by <a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Godsgrief\" title=\"Durran Godsgrief\">Durran Godsgrief</a>. These include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_II_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran II Durrandon\">Durran II the Devout</a>, Godsgrief's son and successor.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(Bronze-Axe)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (Bronze-Axe)\">Durran Bronze-Axe</a>, who reigned a century after Durran the Devout.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(the_Dour)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (the Dour)\">Durran the Dour</a>, who slew the <a href=\"/index.php/Lun_the_Last\" title=\"Lun the Last\">Lun the Last</a>, King of the Giants.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(the_Ravenfriend)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (the Ravenfriend)\">Durran the Ravenfriend</a>, who saw the founding of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Maldon_Massey\" title=\"Maldon Massey\">Maldon Massey</a>'s castle Stonedance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(the_Young)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (the Young)\">Durran the Young</a>, also known as the <i>Butcher Boy</i>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(the_Fair)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (the Fair)\">Durran the Fair</a>, who annexed the <a href=\"/index.php/Tarth\" title=\"Tarth\">Kingdom of Tarth</a> by marrying <a href=\"/index.php/Edwyn_Evenstar\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Edwyn Evenstar\">Edwyn Evenstar</a>'s daughter.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_X_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran X Durrandon\">Durran X</a>, who extended the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_the_Storm\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kingdom of the Storm\">Kingdom of the Storm</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Rush\" title=\"Blackwater Rush\">Blackwater Rush</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_XI_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran XI Durrandon\">Durran XI the Dim</a>, grandson of Durran X.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_XXI_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran XXI Durrandon\">Durran XXI</a>, who reigned during the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_Invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal Invasion\">Andal Invasion</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_Durrandon_(The_Third)\" title=\"Durran Durrandon (The Third)\">Durran the Third</a>, who invaded <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> twice but was defeated by <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_XXIV_Durrandon\" title=\"Durran XXIV Durrandon\">Durran XXIV</a>, also known as Durran Half-Blood, whose mother was <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Durran_Durrandon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Durran_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Durran (disambiguation)\">Durran (disambiguation)</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404112657\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusio